FBIS4-7330 "dreas083_g_94008" FBIS-EAS-94-083 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 SOUTHEAST ASIA Burma Official Appointments Announced by SLORC Official Appointments Announced by SLORC Maung Aye Appointed Vice Chairman BK2704140194 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 27 Apr 94 BK2704140194 Rangoon Radio Burma Burmese BFN [Declaration No. 2/94 of the State Law and Order Restoration Council; issued on 27 April 1994] [Text] Appointment of vice chairman of the State Law and Order Restoration Council [SLORC]. The SLORC has appointed General Maung Aye, SLORC member, deputy commander in chief of the defense services, and Army commander in chief, as the vice chairman of SLORC. By the authority vested in me, Signed; Khin Nyunt, Lieutenant General, secretary-1 of the SLORC.
